<body>
    <h1>Task 14 - Technical Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h2 local-id=3D"228615434c07" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-1.Intr=
oduction"><strong>1. Introduction</strong></h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"91d005740b68" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-1.1Purpose"><s=
trong>1.1 Purpose</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"7c26dad1ea80">This document provides a detailed technical im=
plementation of a <strong>Multi-VPC AWS Network Architecture with Cross-Reg=
ion VPC Peering</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"67ea895eec2f">It is intended for:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f4183acd6ee5">
<li local-id=3D"c1ced7780db0">
<p local-id=3D"0fe5e4d93254">CTOs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7a0213c052bb">
<p local-id=3D"86b4ca8d7a36">Solution Architects</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1e25fd28bd3e">
<p local-id=3D"1ffc6ea167b0">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6544cc7bfe64">
<p local-id=3D"ee0269c89f7a">Cloud Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a4eea50e7d5f">
<p local-id=3D"498c9838a05a">Infrastructure Teams</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"2c50d230c10a">The document demonstrates how multiple VPCs ac=
ross regions can be interconnected securely and efficiently.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"7841751e9bc7">
<h3 local-id=3D"50ddd2cbaff7" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-1.2Scope"><str=
ong>1.2 Scope</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"cd87911edd91">This document covers:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"4895b667e6d7">
<li local-id=3D"9cceaf773ee4">
<p local-id=3D"3ea24a7617a2">Network design using <strong>Class A and Class=
 B IP ranges</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7e5d0347201a">
<p local-id=3D"d136322c0015">Creation of <strong>multiple VPCs across regio=
ns</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"33727b4e7c57">
<p local-id=3D"fb020cab82bd">Implementation of <strong>cross-region VPC pee=
ring</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aec195a30783">
<p local-id=3D"d05114cf4ae8">Configuration of <strong>route tables</strong>=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5ba3afa0c80a">
<p local-id=3D"45f9a511ad84">Deployment of <strong>EC2 instances</strong></=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c9ce037b9026">
<p local-id=3D"8c52557a5107">Validation of <strong>network connectivity</st=
rong></p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"19a92a141d30">
<h2 local-id=3D"23371f7aa5b3" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-2.OverviewofDe=
vOpsProject"><strong>2. Overview of DevOps Project</strong></h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"10eded218b96" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-2.1Definition"=
><strong>2.1 Definition</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"fc20fbf0232c">This project demonstrates a <strong>cloud netw=
orking DevOps implementation</strong> where infrastructure is designed, dep=
loyed, and validated using AWS services.</p>
<p local-id=3D"f7da57f98c14"><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3f63aef95a10">
<li local-id=3D"bcb190f1e2b7">
<p local-id=3D"857a321ee31d">Scalable network architecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"240e3917350e">
<p local-id=3D"9cbd08ddaba6">Isolation using multiple VPCs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7656d7bccc0a">
<p local-id=3D"ed79b9bc0670">Secure communication via private IPs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b0bbc70cce84">
<p local-id=3D"f488bf3a010d">Real-world enterprise design simulation</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"fbaa97068ec5">
<h3 local-id=3D"3657390d5c46" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-2.2KeyPrincipl=
es(AWSWell-ArchitectedFramework)"><strong>2.2 Key Principles (AWS Well-Arch=
itected Framework)</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"d532c752e742">
<li local-id=3D"18c191606bf8">
<p local-id=3D"1fb91cf1925c"><strong>Operational Excellence:</strong> Prope=
r naming, structured VPC creation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"adfe4997ff80">
<p local-id=3D"11252ad2c207"><strong>Security:</strong> Private IP communic=
ation, controlled access (SSH only)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dfb46834da14">
<p local-id=3D"2d8eb05df5fb"><strong>Reliability:</strong> Independent VPCs=
 reduce failure impact</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dc85cc210c3f">
<p local-id=3D"b3a1f789fceb"><strong>Performance Efficiency:</strong> Regio=
n-based deployment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cdadf8b02809">
<p local-id=3D"97a5c82813f5"><strong>Cost Optimization:</strong> t3.micro i=
nstances used</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9ad6ab07e232">
<p local-id=3D"06994f594807"><strong>Sustainability:</strong> Minimal resou=
rce usage</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9dc058201149">
<h3 local-id=3D"536a9c7d6e6e" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-2.3GoalsandObj=
ectives"><strong>2.3 Goals and Objectives</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"42e45ce05583">
<li local-id=3D"022f247bd028">
<p local-id=3D"690251fcd0e0">Design multi-VPC architecture</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a352986e505d">
<p local-id=3D"9716eb80b603">Implement cross-region VPC peering</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ebc4b2f32160">
<p local-id=3D"f1f851220e75">Enable secure inter-VPC communication</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e9551b662a75">
<p local-id=3D"a1f875fcc3b4">Validate connectivity using EC2 instances</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e5c8c59e5c86">
<h3 local-id=3D"5b7303833fb0" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-2.4Constraints=
andAssumptions"><strong>2.4 Constraints and Assumptions</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"8697a56e5209"><strong>Constraints:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"bc1be43e1d48">
<li local-id=3D"c05b8e31e481">
<p local-id=3D"862eeaf702f3">Limited time (3 hours)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9ad74fe4da41">
<p local-id=3D"cae49d58bb8f">AWS Free Tier usage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"96f01378a54b">
<p local-id=3D"c9083630f263">Minimal infrastructure</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"fad4e69e6e7f"><strong>Assumptions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"d850eed8cf8f">
<li local-id=3D"5f3db0d54463">
<p local-id=3D"1d5c4a8397fe">All VPCs are correctly CIDR planned</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9e0dba64c6b6">
<p local-id=3D"ba761613e39c">No IP overlap</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b6974031343c">
<p local-id=3D"9bfa5caf85c5">Security groups allow SSH traffic</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"c47027c89280">
<h2 local-id=3D"c10499ab77aa" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-3.Architecture=
andInfrastructure"><strong>3. Architecture and Infrastructure</strong></h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"12db62ac8f93" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-3.1Infrastruct=
ureOverview"><strong>3.1 Infrastructure Overview</strong></h3><span class=
=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedd=
ed-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=
=3D"diagram-export-3-22-2026-1_13_25-AM-20260321-194341.png" width=3D"468" =
loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"ffaa9cd1ab6b2fd6220fe601c7075db9e85029818374544d7b9=
e2cc8d96c3666" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download=
/attachments/1886289995/diagram-export-3-22-2026-1_13_25-AM-20260321-194341=
.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1774122239455&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&=
amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"1083" data-width=3D"1263" data-unresolved-comm=
ent-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1885602115" data-linked-resource=
-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resourc=
e-default-alias=3D"diagram-export-3-22-2026-1_13_25-AM-20260321-194341.png"=
 data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-c=
