<p local-id=3D"308d9006f38e"></p>
<ul local-id=3D"65f1f0802512">
<li local-id=3D"e59e4bba3d5c">
<p local-id=3D"d94352f33d2f"><strong>Region 1 (us-east-1):</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"acf6bca78d43">
<li local-id=3D"d45e5e25b165">
<p local-id=3D"c085d854ea99">HQ VPC =E2=86=92 <code>10.0.0.0/22</code> (Cla=
ss A)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"29bc7f99d494">
<p local-id=3D"317573cab2cf">Subnets:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"5954ce0f8775">
<li local-id=3D"405b0c32e898">
<p local-id=3D"b52934b0531d">Server Subnet</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0b088aa2196e">
<p local-id=3D"93714c15fa11">Management Subnet</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"cbf1b0149ff6">
<p local-id=3D"55c8efe7a4c6"><strong>Region 2 (us-east-2):</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"b0c7ece377ae">
<li local-id=3D"849b95f4bd01">
<p local-id=3D"ab9314183da9">Office A =E2=86=92 <code>172.16.1.0/26</code><=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6aae36a3faec">
<p local-id=3D"595abadc0f70">Office B =E2=86=92 <code>172.16.2.0/26</code><=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"315de50d386e">
<p local-id=3D"58d1daaa613f">Office C =E2=86=92 <code>172.16.3.0/26</code><=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a1f830cad7e0">
<p local-id=3D"ec60db09a5e4">Office D =E2=86=92 <code>172.16.4.0/26</code><=
/p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"a9a7570bb832">
<p local-id=3D"0a385df991cf"><strong>Connectivity:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"7c662c5c8ef2">
<li local-id=3D"73f37ef355bd">
<p local-id=3D"760c0b3507f5">HQ =E2=86=94 All Branch Offices via VPC Peerin=
g</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"b8d0f450d4d2">
<h3 local-id=3D"a1633a8a34c8" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-3.2Environment=
s"><strong>3.2 Environments</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"d1dc880bcaf9">
<li local-id=3D"ff2356843f08">
<p local-id=3D"8b2603288444">Single environment (Test/Validation)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"75e082e75bc1">
<p local-id=3D"1e76ecf7cc71">Used for connectivity verification</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"09d56e87f28f">
<h3 local-id=3D"e2811efda77d" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-3.3ToolsandTec=
hnologies"><strong>3.3 Tools and Technologies</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"f1acc1f84fa7">
<li local-id=3D"405c720bb2e2">
<p local-id=3D"65912a366bce">AWS VPC</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2ec5d09d2b3b">
<p local-id=3D"a450fe684482">EC2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0c4dcb60e950">
<p local-id=3D"fe2d5d3a9dc6">VPC Peering</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"36918923bf72">
<p local-id=3D"2c9d375ebb6f">Route Tables</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d72f85a8778a">
<p local-id=3D"0cca113279ef">Security Groups</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0819f0409b4e">
<p local-id=3D"c61e628179be">Ubuntu (Linux)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1b7e32f1430b">
<p local-id=3D"fca54018b04f">Telnet (Connectivity Testing)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"453c6ddd71a1">
<h3 local-id=3D"b0b14f907e82" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-3.4Application=
Architecture&amp;UserRequestFlow"><strong>3.4 Application Architecture &amp=
; User Request Flow</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"cb7b9b85d374">User =E2=86=92 EC2 Instance (HQ) =E2=86=92 VPC=
 Peering =E2=86=92 Branch Office EC2<br>
=E2=86=92 Communication over Private IP (Port 22)</p>
<hr local-id=3D"881c89d01c07">
<h2 local-id=3D"3c32b7e51ceb" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-4.DevelopmentP=
ractices"><strong>4. Development Practices</strong></h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"239565b4f6c3" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-4.1VersionCont=
rol"><strong>4.1 Version Control</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"40f5e5d0964d">Not applicable (Infrastructure task)</p>
<hr local-id=3D"74ff9de1412d">
<h3 local-id=3D"e8bfc12bbcf8" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-4.2ContinuousI=
ntegration"><strong>4.2 Continuous Integration</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"bf18b2ab2d02">Manual infrastructure deployment via AWS Conso=
le</p>
<hr local-id=3D"c647cb5ec66a">
<h3 local-id=3D"6eacd7a9acdd" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-4.3AutomatedTe=
sting"><strong>4.3 Automated Testing</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"4d32c48fadba">Connectivity testing using:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">telnet =
&lt;private-ip&gt; 22</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"8e62c23e16c9">
<h3 local-id=3D"c97c404aef5e" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-4.4CodeQuality=
"><strong>4.4 Code Quality</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"7a6c8946d41a">Validated through:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b1e9b8559353">
<li local-id=3D"a5e88f7feca7">
<p local-id=3D"513148967ba1">Successful SSH banner response</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"983ddc2c7241">
<p local-id=3D"016896d6b9fd">No connection timeout</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"1bdff85ff8f2">
<h2 local-id=3D"72272267f65c" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-5.Deploymentan=
dReleaseManagement"><strong>5. Deployment and Release Management</strong></=
h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"adafb4b9a811" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-5.1DeploymentS=
trategy"><strong>5.1 Deployment Strategy</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"5468b240ac88">
<li local-id=3D"a269af0e8dbf">
<p local-id=3D"0e99734118cf">Step-by-step manual deployment:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"fe2ec4bbca45">
<li local-id=3D"d29e7b912219">
<p local-id=3D"b285d8d97dcf">VPC =E2=86=92 Subnets =E2=86=92 Peering =E2=86=
=92 Routing =E2=86=92 EC2</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a81844615b37">
<h3 local-id=3D"57a645dcd5a2" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-5.2Configurati=
