<hr local-id=3D"e507ce480097">
<h2 local-id=3D"1cb2298ea9ed" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-10.Implementat=
ionTimeline"><strong>10. Implementation Timeline</strong></h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"f607b1a6a949" id=3D"Task14-TechnicalDocument-10.1Milestones=
"><strong>10.1 Milestones</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"4d0159feed91">
<li local-id=3D"40141adf8f20">
<p local-id=3D"96a280597c14">Phase 1: Network Design (30 mins)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9facadeef92d">
<p local-id=3D"c54da5d75a1b">Phase 2: VPC Creation (45 mins)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1236941d5529">
<p local-id=3D"66473f7bb527">Phase 3: VPC Peering (30 mins)</p></li>
